  three-portfolios chart (which needs about that much), but the inflation
  chart's content is only ~680px tall, leaving ~90px of empty space. Let me
  add a small `postMessage` self-resize so each interactive sizes its own
  iframe precisely.

First, add the listener in the parent (build.py SITE_JS):

